{
  "stem": "25591.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Renee. ?] We are our brothers' and sister' keepers, whether these are Buddhists in Burma or Tibet, whether these are Christians who are persecuted, whether these are people who are persecuted because of their pigmentation-- the color of their skin-- whether they are persecuted because of their ethnic background like the nightmares we had been through in the former Yugoslavia, we need to speak up and stop these outrages because the bell always sounds for us.",
      "word_count": 76
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We cannot be bystanders.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's not enough not to be a perpetrator.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You must not be a bystander.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The prime obligation of every human being is to speak out against injustice committed against any other human being.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the more different that human being is from you, the greater your obligation to speak out for that human being and to defend him.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Raoul Wallenberg was not Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was not persecuted.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He was a-- he was a Christian Swede who was very wealthy and very safe and very secure, and yet he left all of that behind and risked his life, and paid with his life for this message-- that we are our brother's keeper.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I don't think there is anything you didn't ask me, but I want to say that I can't begin to thank Steven Spielberg and the Shoah Project for doing this.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What you're doing personally, what Steven is doing, what-- what all of your associates are doing is one of the great historic gestures to make this world a more sane place.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as a-- as a humble worker in the vineyard of this enterprise, I want to thank you very much for doing it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's a pleasure.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
